	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well first thing I would do if your a 6th lvl warrior is to put the high damage low delay weapons in the bank. Buy some fs weapons or have your main give your twink the weapons and go to town. Below 20th level its hard enough to get all your weapon skills built up with killing your mobs too quickly. You don't want to be 30th lvl with low weapon skills as well as low skill in taunt. I wouldn't want to group with a tank that can't hold agro.  Other than that for equipment upgrades ditch the serp bracer and bracer of erollisi and get crafted bracers and upgrade to cougar claw earrings. The few points in AC will add up and are of more benefit than stat increasing items at your level.<br>&nbsp;<br>Cannis Skywise 47 Ranger<br>Razer Darkreaver 42st Sk<br>Jeetkundo 20th Monk<br>Mikaraz 26th Warrior</td></tr>
