	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey.<br><br>You can indeed make bandages, using the tailoring skill.  <br><br><LI><b>Starting with spiderling silks:</b><br>Spiderling silk(1) + Spiderling silk(1) = Silk thread(1)<br>Silk thread(1) + Silk thread(1) = Silk bandage(1)<br><br><br>Making silk threads trivials at a tailoring skill of 17.  However, this (and making silk swatches) never fails.<br>Making silk bandages trivials at a tailoring skill of 21.<br><br>Silk bandages are identical to normal bandages, except that they're lighter.  <br><br>Hope this helps.<br><br>AlAaraaf.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>"Te aurdire no possum. Musa sapienum fixa est in aura."</td></tr>
